WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: leaving a tailnet — a clean uninstall on each platform.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: tailscale logout first, so the operator sees the departure.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: apt purge tailscale on linux removes the daemon and CLI.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: state lives under /var/lib/tailscale — remove it explicitly.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: macOS — brew uninstall and rm the Application Support dir.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: windows — the MSI uninstaller plus the per-user state dir.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: no on-disk material remains; the preauth key is single-use.
